<div><head>《虞盤佑孝子傳》</head>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1333_CHANT_001-1a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2c1333_CHANT_001-1a" ed="CHANT" n="001-1a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1333_CHANT_001-1a.2">虞盤佑孝子傳<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1333_CHANT_001-1a.3">曾子以藜蒸不熟遣妻。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1333_CHANT_001-1a.4">《御覽》九百九十八。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1333_CHANT_001-1a.5">華光，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1333_CHANT_001-1a.6">字榮祖，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1333_CHANT_001-1a.7">彭城人。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1333_CHANT_001-1a.8">父亡六日，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1333_CHANT_001-1a.9">年四歲問父所在，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1333_CHANT_001-1a.10">母親送光至父冢，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1333_CHANT_001-1a.11">光再拜伏哭，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1333_CHANT_001-1a.12">欲留冢下，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1333_CHANT_001-1a.13">母抱歸，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1333_CHANT_001-1a.14">悲咽，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1333_CHANT_001-1a.15">三日不食。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1333_CHANT_001-1a.16">至年七歲，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1333_CHANT_001-1a.17">欲見父像，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1333_CHANT_001-1a.18">雇畫師畫其父像，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1333_CHANT_001-1a.19">朝夕拜謁如父。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1333_CHANT_001-1a.20">《御覽》四百十二。<lb/></seg>
</p>
